headline: Jabil Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., July 17, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $0.08 per share of common stock to shareholders of record as of August 15, 2025. The dividend is payable on September 3, 2025.

headline: Jabil Announces $1 Billion Share Repurchase Authorization
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., July 17, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) today announced that its Board of Directors has authorized a share repurchase program of up to $1 billion in common stock. The shares will be repurchased from time to time using various methods, including in the open market at the Company’s discretion and subject to market conditions.
